The paper proposes a novel latent dynamic model that uses recurrent neural networks and non-parametric Gaussian process to capture nonlinear, non-Markovian, long short-term time-dependent dynamics. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), systems and control (cs.SD), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV).
